description:
Thyatira - the fourth of the seven Churches of Revelation is located in the modern city of Akhisar. It would have been a particularly hard place to maintain ones Christian faith. It was a manufacturing city, known for its trade unions and the description of the church is arguable worse than Pergamos. After compromise comes apostasy and corruption, but in the midst of this bleak outlook there is still strong hope in this message!
